title: Kiss: Man, Person, Dark Skin Tone
description: Represents a kiss between a man and a person with a dark skin tone. It signifies affection, romance, and connection, adaptable to different gender presentations.
apple_vendor_description: The kiss man emoji with dark skin tone on Apple devices presents a warm and affectionate gesture, with the man's lips slightly pursed and angled towards a kiss. Apple's design imbues this emoji with a soft, rounded quality and gentle highlights, suggesting tenderness and intimacy. It's a charming way to express love, affection, or a playful goodbye in messages shared on Apple devices.
